title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show NOV-28-2014 FRI
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show NOV-28-2014 FRI

The Glenn Beck Program
        
      
      Thanksgiving After Action Report;
  
         Truth is a Casualty of Ferguson Movement 11/28/14

Friday, November 28, 2014 

Buck Sexton fills in for Glenn, 

     covering the history of Black Friday/Black Friday madness,

       a comparison of Ferguson protesters and Black Friday protesters,

         and the moral position in race relations. 

   
Plus, Teddy Schwarzman discusses his new film 

       "The Imitation Game." 



              That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!
